# Daily Family Briefing — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to ~/.env (your home directory, NOT inside this repo)
# and fill in your real values.
#
# For GitHub Actions, add each of these as a GitHub Secret:
#   Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions → New repository secret
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# The Gmail address used to SEND the briefing email
BRIEFING_SENDER=your-email@gmail.com

# Comma-separated list of addresses to receive the briefing
BRIEFING_RECIPIENTS=your-email@gmail.com,partner@gmail.com

# Google Calendar IDs for the two personal calendars
# For Gmail accounts, the Calendar ID is just the Gmail address
JOHN_CALENDAR_ID=your-email@gmail.com
SUTTON_CALENDAR_ID=partner@gmail.com

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# These two are generated by setup.py and should be added as GitHub Secrets.
# They are base64-encoded — DO NOT set them in plain text here.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# GOOGLE_TOKEN_JSON=<base64 value printed by setup.py>
# GOOGLE_CREDENTIALS_JSON=<base64 value printed by setup.py>
